{"tid":1520804,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港教育最大危機] 警子女警報器係學校特權階級工具","createTime":"2019-08-31T03:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T10:15:39.000Z","uid":41458,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bb28578c9ce21aa736dc0987e8c9e53d70b74aac","tid":1520804,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:14:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190831/20759416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190831%2F20759416&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2WWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=3b9cbc22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190831%2F20759416&h=814307e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190831/20759416</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">【本報訊】警察連番濫捕並暴力對待市民，令警民關係嚴重撕裂，警察員佐級協會聲稱有警員子女淪為欺凌對象，更擔心下星期一新學期開始，校園欺凌情況加劇。警方有鑑於此，近日向警務人員的未成年子女提供個人便攜式警報器，以便他們一旦遭受襲擊或欺凌時可以使用。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個警報器好容易就可以被濫用<br />\n令警仔女成為學校內既特權階級<br />\n以後佢地返學可以做大佬, 欺凌其他人, 甚至老師校長<br />\n邊個佢睇唔順眼就按掣, 等黑警做野, 拉人入獄<br />\n呢個警報器對香港既教育制度, 以至全香港, 為害無窮!"},{"pid":"9a86f425769eec6503d2753c695a9cd29ece21be","tid":1520804,"uid":112171,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:22:28.000Z","msg":"校園欺凌一直都有，點解之前比人欺凌個班冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，香港軍政府嘅接班人有特權?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba046b1e3b935d487659df997c1bc482b74567c","tid":1520804,"uid":78429,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:23:03.000Z","msg":"睇落應該好易偷"},{"pid":"e623c9b938b21cf751dc5773f6462ccf983f54b7","tid":1520804,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b172eb80099a42c25f70fbdd9735621c9c394ef","tid":1520804,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">［<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">梁天琦</span>］一 個 月 前 的 忠 告 ：<br />\n不是以自己寶貴的生命和他們對賭</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1520801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1520801</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0d86986459b0304f4e16109fd541bb519aff95ac","tid":1520804,"uid":139173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUpTHxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUpTHxB.jpg&h=6bd49a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n831唔係end game<br />\n九月有機場有三罷<br />\n<br />\n政府急我地就拖慢<br />\n記住不受傷不被捕<br />\n九月份繼續齊上齊落<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n天龍人？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08605e034b491b7898d59e875367f2095b86432","tid":1520804,"uid":163734,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9a86f425769eec6503d2753c695a9cd29ece21be","tid":1520804,"uid":112171,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:22:28.000Z","msg":"校園欺凌一直都有，點解之前比人欺凌個班冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，香港軍政府嘅接班人有特權?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:26:57.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山嗰單被人咁欺凌，都唔見政府有做野去幫，而家未開學就警班狗仔女被欺凌。 屌你老母啦。 唔撚同呢班仆街玩呀"},{"pid":"5dc740ba3d49a74f376f9644b50d407ea6213a71","tid":1520804,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"國際文宣組做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c3c6ebd8d337af05b03fc82edae067ad90a739","tid":1520804,"uid":37719,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"Miss任屌<br />\n女同學任屌<br />\n三千後宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔比就加兩錢肉緊扮比人恰<br />\n搞鳩你全家"},{"pid":"a7b8127522995f0ea64a1d74ab3c0d6914f58a99","tid":1520804,"uid":167192,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:34:25.000Z","msg":"其實咁做只會令狗仔女更容易被標籤同欺凌<br />\nSelf-fulfilling Prophecy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e721513b3e851c60fa1dbbd24061a998839f7f","tid":1520804,"uid":182025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:36:18.000Z","msg":"繼續推出國際 話俾全世界教育界知 香港係警察國家 所有警察特權學校自己玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e23283de56afad77df4b28bd30b65ca41a0425","tid":1520804,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:37:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1afd40e8ce4b3e87c479b0f92bb1c8cc7def31f9","tid":1520804,"uid":166947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a7b8127522995f0ea64a1d74ab3c0d6914f58a99","tid":1520804,"uid":167192,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:34:25.000Z","msg":"其實咁做只會令狗仔女更容易被標籤同欺凌<br />\nSelf-fulfilling Prophecy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:38:37.000Z","msg":"全校得你一個on99拎住個警報器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話其他人會點睇"},{"pid":"2767ea756ec2f97cba6c828639f461f9fd7f3a71","tid":1520804,"uid":140335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"狗仔狗爸都攞正牌係全香港亂打人<br />\n係學校見到唔鐘意嘅<br />\n又可以打佢 打完同佢講番句<br />\n你敢還手我就㩒制<br />\n<br />\n啲阿sir miss話佢幾句<br />\n又可以作下話佢歧視我係狗仔<br />\n到時又逼學校炒人<br />\n<br />\n變成狗仔狗女係學校又變左另一惡勢力<br />\n學校真係社會縮影"},{"pid":"ae40f9734663f5dc5d2af1b60e0d79fa00d5c04f","tid":1520804,"uid":31609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c206e5c4184eb5b49dbfaaa5a322971d4e1522","tid":1520804,"uid":288304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"守護學生妹行動 <br />\n<br />\n一開學啲狗仔會似住自己有特權，四圍去搞啲女同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如其他同學在學校被警務人員子女欺凌，大家一定要出聲<br />\n<br />\n我已經預計到，佢地會對其他男同學陏手陏腳，對女同學就摸手摸腳<br />\n<br />\n「你係唔係唔畀我打？你係唔係唔畀我摸？我同學校講你歧視我」<br />\n<br />\n大家千祈唔好啞忍，咁嘅欺凌行為只會越嚟越嚴重"},{"pid":"f9272a5ba00bf7cd38e870d869abe21d2c813211","tid":1520804,"uid":313663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"到時啲狗仔狗女周圍打鳩人，一還拖就禁警報器"},{"pid":"5b2b9aa181083d8133cab3ad8205efde45a1b3be","tid":1520804,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:43:53.000Z","msg":"教育制度都限制，其實學校係咪變咗再教育營"},{"pid":"1f39daea3f53336f4843039d1b75881c14593ff7","tid":1520804,"uid":81698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:45:01.000Z","msg":"有警報器=搵到欺凌對像"},{"pid":"e4aab716ecc9dcd9b011168a8d4ba6f6ab0a7ab1","tid":1520804,"uid":136303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"多謝幫我地起埋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbf146418d3e7ef68bb740a935e84e951b1380e","tid":1520804,"uid":175346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:46:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2911072052a00eb68c28ed3b4a01afe10adddbb","tid":1520804,"uid":67697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:53:12.000Z","msg":"學佢地老豆咁<br />\n唔聽話就按警報器屈個細路蝦佢<br />\n根據現時社會風氣 老師信狗仔 <br />\n校長發現細路被屈後叫佢和解 唔好搞咁多野<br />\n警犬win<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193163971fb0d6606d21a5dca87d0b313e13bd06","tid":1520804,"uid":67697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"唔知上個學期被欺凌既普通小朋友<br />\n見到狗仔有掣㩒 但自己無<br />\n個心情係點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d882706d8efd9f3013e306d241fcda8449a41cd","tid":1520804,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7c3c6ebd8d337af05b03fc82edae067ad90a739","tid":1520804,"uid":37719,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"Miss任屌<br />\n女同學任屌<br />\n三千後宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔比就加兩錢肉緊扮比人恰<br />\n搞鳩你全家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:01:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母睇字都好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攞住個警報器係度屌靚女miss"},{"pid":"a8a8cc293f562999f8bba87eeab5f2d585102801","tid":1520804,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}